node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
# Exclude TS incremental state too: with `**/dist` ignored, a stale
# `*.tsbuildinfo` copied from the host would make `tsc --build` believe a
# package is up-to-date and skip emitting its `dist/`, breaking the image build.
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
coverage
**/.vitest-cache
**/.turbo
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
.env
.env.*
!**/.env.example
